# Movie Rating Tool

A Python package for rating movies, comparing your ratings with online (IMDb-style) ratings, seeing statistics and charts.

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME/movie-rating-tool.git
cd movie-rating-tool
uv pip install -e .
```
